## 2. Content (all rights reserved)

**Copyright (c) 2026 Andrew Knight. All Rights Reserved.**

### What counts as Content

Content means the creative material made available through Auto Panda Motive,
including without limitation:

- Writing, stories, hooks, and other prose
- Photographs and images of vehicles and related subjects
- Embedded or linked media presented as part of the site
- Car names, personal narratives, and other original text in content files

Content includes files under paths such as `src/content/` and
`public/images/cars/`, along with any other non-Software creative material
added to this project.

### Permissions

You may view Content through the published website for personal, non-commercial
enjoyment.

Unless Andrew Knight gives you prior written permission, you may **not**:

- Copy, reproduce, or republish Content
- Distribute, sell, or license Content
- Modify Content or create derivative works from it
- Use Content in another website, publication, product, or commercial project

### Forking this repository

You may fork or clone this repository to study or reuse the Software. If you
publish a fork, replace the Content with your own creative material. Do not
republish Andrew Knight's Content as your own.

